  meaning "external_knowledge_source"
    gloss "a source outside the local seed, such as Wikidata, Wiktionary, WordNet, Wikipedia, a thesaurus, or a dictionary. It is a semantic grounding artifact because source responses can be converted to Links Notation and linked back to the meanings they support."
